arg.description:
The FilePath, FileType, RecordVideo, Fps, Quality, RecordAudio, Bitrate, TimingReminder, WaterPrint, WaterPrintText, MicVolume and SpeakerVolume can be set.
            Spelling needs to be consistent with those listed above, case sensitive.
            One or more can be specified, use json form, E.g {"FilePath":"ogv", "Fps":"10"}

The FilePath, FileType, RecordVideo, Fps, Quality, RecordAudio, Bitrate, TimingPause, WaterPrint and WaterPrintText,
            MinFreeSpace, MaxSaveDays, MaxFileSize and MaxRecordPerUser can be set. Spelling needs to be consistent with those listed above, case sensitive.
            One or more can be specified, use json form, E.g {"FilePath":"ogv", "Fps":"10"}
